  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>The Naughty List Curse is a story-telling horror game about saving Christmas and the secrets hidden behind the darkness.</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Plot:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let the elf guide you through the world of magic where everthing you think you know will change. Fight against the darkness and help to give Christmas back its sparkle. <strong><i>You can run and you can hide, but can you save Christmas?</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Specialities:</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short Christmas horror game (circa 90 minutes).</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Storyline in first person.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Christmas decorations and snow.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Christmas weapons.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Trigger Warning:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game may trigger seizures to people with epilepsy.</p>",
